OL,3,CMan freed from prison under early
OL,4,Crelease scheme charged with murder
OL,6,FA man freed from prison under the
OL,7,FGovernment's early release scheme has
OL,8,Fbeen charged with murder.
OL,10,FThe man, who cannot be named for legal
OL,11,Freasons, was released as part of
OL,12,Fefforts to reduce prison overcrowding,
OL,13,Faccording to The Times.
OL,15,FIt is the most serious offence alleged
OL,16,Fto have been committed by someone
OL,17,Freleased under the scheme, which
OL,18,Fallows some offenders to be freed
OL,19,Fafter serving 40% of their sentence,
OL,20,Frather than 50%.
