OL,3,CMan freed from prison under early
OL,4,Crelease scheme charged with murder
OL,6,FThe scheme applies to prisoners
OL,7,Fserving a determinate sentence, the
OL,8,Fmost common form of prison sentence,
OL,9,Fbut excludes those convicted of sexual
OL,10,Foffences, domestic abuse and national
OL,11,Fsecurity-related offences such as
OL,12,Fterrorism.
OL,14,FViolent offenders sentenced to more
OL,15,Fthan four years are also excluded.
OL,17,FOnce released, they remain on licence
OL,18,Ffor the rest of their sentence and can
OL,19,Fbe recalled to prison if they breach
OL,20,Fthe terms of their release or commit
OL,21,Ffurther offences.
