OL,3,CMan freed from prison under early
OL,4,Crelease scheme charged with murder
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with the
OL,8,Fvictim's family. This Government
OL,9,Finherited a prisons crisis, days away
OL,10,Ffrom running out of space which would
OL,11,Fhave brought the justice system to a
OL,12,Fstandstill, stopped the police from
OL,13,Fbeing able to make arrests and led to
OL,14,Funchecked criminality on our streets.
OL,16,F"Public safety will always be our top
OL,17,Fpriority, and we are building 14,000
OL,18,Fmore prison places to keep dangerous
OL,19,Foffenders locked up."
