OL,3,CMan freed from prison under early
OL,4,Crelease scheme charged with murder
OL,6,FSome 38,042 prisoners have been
OL,7,Freleased under the scheme, introduced
OL,8,Fshortly after Labour came to power
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FOfficials had warned that male prisons
OL,12,Fwere on track to completely run out of
OL,13,Fspace prior to the policy being
OL,14,Fintroduced by the now-Home Secretary
OL,15,FShabana Mahmood.
OL,17,FFigures released on Thursday showed
OL,18,Fthe overall prison population had
OL,19,Ffallen from its February 2024 peak of
OL,20,F88,439, reaching 87,465 in September
OL,21,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
