OL,6,FBut this was still higher than the
OL,7,Ftotal prison population in September
OL,8,F2024.
OL,10,FRecalls to prison have also increased,
OL,11,Freaching 11,041 between April and June
OL,12,F2025, a 13% increase on the same
OL,13,Fperiod in 2024.
OL,15,FRecalls are at a "historically high"
OL,16,Flevel, the Ministry of Justice said,
OL,17,Fand the rise is "likely to be
OL,18,Fassociated" with the Government's
OL,19,Fearly release scheme that began in
OL,20,FSeptember 2024.
