OL,6,FIt also attributed the rise to a
OL,7,Fchange in the law to recall under the
OL,8,FConservative government in April 2024,
OL,9,Fwhere offenders sentenced to less than
OL,10,F12 months will serve a short fixed
OL,11,Fterm when recalled, instead of serving
OL,12,Fthe rest of their full jail term.
